android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from external storage.

Ether can be transferred between accounts and used to compensate participant mining nodes for computations performed. Ethereum provides a decentralised Turing-complete virtual machine, the Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM), which can execute scripts using an international network of public nodes. Gas, an internal transaction pricing mechanism, is used to mitigate spam and allocate resources on the network."

playstore_details.title: Lead Wallet (BETA) - Store & Swap Cryptocurrencies
playstore_details.description:
Cryptocurrencies, DeFi and NFT Access Wallet: Bitcoin (BTC), Litecoin (LTC), Ethereum (ETH), Tether (USDT) Tron (TRX)
Lead Wallet is the simplest and most secure multi cryptocurrency wallet  that allow users to store, spend, stake, and swap cryptocurrencies seamlessly at anytime, and also support easy DeFi and NFT access. This multi-functional crypto wallet app supports most 100+ cryptocurrencies across different Blockchains. The Lead team perform updates regularly to add new crypto coins/tokens and features that makes managing ones crypto portfolio easy and secure. Lead wallet is simply the gateway to blockchain technology and cryptocurrencies.
Lead Wallet is fully decentralized and secure and there is regular auditing which ensures that users have total control to send, receive, stake, swap and store all sorts of digital assets. In addition, users have full control of their private keys which is only stored on a user's device.
The wallet also allow users to navigate the Decentralized world of Finance (DeFi), Gaming collectibles (NFT) and other related DApps which can be easily accessed on the blockchain.
The wallet also feature an inbuilt Web3 Browser that allow users to interact with DApps, right from the application.
Lead Wallet Major High Points:
Support crypto-to-crypto swap and fiat-to-crypto conversion.
The wallet supports all Ethereum based tokens thus allowing users to hold and participate in ERC20 or ERC223 based token sale or airdrops. The wallet also allow users to determine gas prices, your gas limits, set custom transaction fees, and transmit data and messages in a way that is easily understandable.

The app also helps to protects your crypto assets via enabling additional security measures, such as app pin and biometrics.
Lead wallet allow users to restore and backup wallets either through a passphrase or private keys within 18 seconds.

Need a Bitcoin Wallet for Android? Use Lead Wallet as either a coin-specific wallet or a  Multi Crypto Wallet!
Lead Wallet was designed from the ground up to help ensure a positive experience for Android users.
Can be used as your Bitcoin and multi coin wallet so you can send, receive, store, and track all your digital assets in one place. Trading Bitcoin and trading crypto directly from the wallet is now possible through Decentralized Exchange support, allowing you to control your digital assets through the secure storage of your private keys on your device.

Features include:
- Ethereum Wallet: send and request ether, ERC20 tokens.
- DApp Browser to instantly buy and sell Bitcoin, Ethereum, and other cryptocurrencies and digital assets; provide liquidity on DEX protocols; and access favorite DApps on the Ethereum Blockchain.
- Support a marketplace where users can make purchase or order for different kinds of goods services with payment made in cryptocurrencies or fiat.
- Swap and Exchange feature that allow users to easily trade against different crypto assets.
- Push notifications 
- Detailed transaction information, including a complete history and the total value of a user's portfolio.
- Easily send and receive assets through QR codes or with copy and paste functions.
- Full security with passcode protection to include additional encryption and protection.
- E-Money / E-Wallet for storing digital money like stable coins 

Supported Cryptocurrencies:
Bitcoin wallet (BTC) 
Litecoin Wallet (LTC) 
Ethereum wallet (ETH) 
Tron Wallet (TRX) 
Dash Wallet (DASH)
Dogecoin Wallet (DOGE)

Lead Wallet supported Stable Coins (ERC20 stable coins)
True USD (TUSD)
Tether (USDT)
Binance USD (BUSD)
Binance GBP (BGBP)
Coinbase USD (USDC)
Gemini USD (GUSD)


If you have any questions, have issues with our crypto wallet, or would like to provide feedback, recommendation or make a request, please contact us via one of the following:
Email: contact@leadwallet.io
Telegram: https://telegram.me/Leadwallet
Telegram Ann: https://telegram.me/Leadwallet_ann
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Leadwallet
